595
00:26:54,579 --> 00:26:56,614
Oh, mijo,
it all happened too fast.

596
00:26:56,681 --> 00:26:58,115
I didn't see him.

597
00:26:59,084 --> 00:27:00,985
I want to help you...

598
00:27:02,621 --> 00:27:04,555
... but I can't.

599
