early that night.

617
00:27:46,463 --> 00:27:48,530
A snowstorm was blowing in--
flew out to beat it.

618
00:27:49,098 --> 00:27:50,331
Missed the miracle.

619
00:27:50,399 --> 00:27:51,800
Must have mixed up my times.

620
00:27:51,868 --> 00:27:53,969
