00:27:54,037 --> 00:27:55,938
Like trying to get Tommy
kicked off the team.

622
00:27:56,006 --> 00:27:57,440
Now hold on.

623
00:27:57,507 --> 00:28:00,042
No, owner said no way.
That Tommy had spunk.

624
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:01,677
The kid was a draw.

625
00:28:02,245 --> 00:28:03,345
You were pissed.

626
00:28:03,413 --> 00:28:05,747
The next day, Tommy's on ice,
and you're lying

627
00:28:05,815 --> 00:28:07,649
- about what you were doing.
- I don't have to listen to this.

628
00:28:07,717 --> 00:28:10,118
How come you don't talk to
your daughter anymore, coach ?

629
00:28:11,053 --> 00:28:12,654
Molly.

630
00:28:13,522 --> 00:28:15,991
Hard as I was on my players,
I was tougher on her.

631
00:28:16,059 --> 00:28:17,592
Or after you iced her boyfriend,

632
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:19,260
