back and forth.</i>

645
00:28:47,724 --> 00:28:49,091
Nothing in the twine.

646
00:28:51,895 --> 00:28:54,998
<i>Oh, and yet another
illegal hit</i>

647
00:28:55,066 --> 00:28:56,366
<i>from Cullen Masters.</i>

648
00:28:56,434 --> 00:28:59,103
<i>I'll tell you,
that's going to draw a penalty.</i>

649
00:28:59,171 --> 00:29:01,406
You're throwing me out
'cause this little freak ?!

650
00:29:01,473 --> 00:29:02,707
Get up, punk !

651
00:29:02,775 --> 00:29:07,012
Catch you alone,
I'm gonna kick your candy-ass!

