00:29:15,154 --> 00:29:17,657
Once chance, Tommy.
Can you do this ?

656
00:29:18,425 --> 00:29:19,826
Yeah, coach.

657
00:29:22,394 --> 00:29:23,731
I got it.

658
00:29:37,579 --> 00:29:38,980
<i>Flanagan shoots.</i>

659
00:29:39,047 --> 00:29:40,581
<i>He's got it !</i>

660
00:29:41,049 --> 00:29:42,483
And he scores !

661
00:29:43,051 --> 00:29:45,888
<i>Little Tommy Flanagan scores !</i>

662
00:29:45,956 --> 00:29:49,092
<i>One nothing at home,
Dock Rats take it !</i>

663
00:29:50,662 --> 00:29:52,496
<i>Little Tommy Flanagan.</i>

664
00:29:52,764 --> 00:29:55,600
<i>Unbelievable !</i>

665
00:29:56,468 --> 00:29:57,969
<i>He is truly...</i>

666
00:29:58,037 --> 00:30:00,239
