Her graduating class, 1980.

682
00:30:43,924 --> 00:30:45,824
December, 1980.

683
00:30:45,892 --> 00:30:47,627
Seven months later
than everybody else.

684
00:30:47,695 --> 00:30:49,498
Straight "A" student...
how does that happen ?

685
00:30:49,566 --> 00:30:51,036
Three days after
Tommy was killed,

686
00:30:51,104 --> 00:30:55,076
