to st. Emily's in Lancaster.

687
00:30:55,443 --> 00:30:57,979
That's where good unwed catholic
girls go to have babies.

688
00:30:58,047 --> 00:30:59,382
No one's supposed
to know about.

689
00:30:59,449 --> 00:31:02,018
So Tommy and Molly
weren't just close.

690
00:31:02,086 --> 00:31:03,754
She was pregnant.

691
00:31:03,822 --> 00:31:05,924
And coach covered it up.

692
00:31:05,992 --> 00:31:07,527
No wonder they don't
talk anymore.

693
00:31:07,595 --> 00:31:09,397
Let's bring Molly back in.

694
00:31:09,465 --> 00:31:12,069
Work both of them
till one of them cracks.

695
00:31:16,155 --> 00:31:17,358
I have to say,

696
00:31:17,459 --> 00:31:20,459
I kinda get what you saw
in Tommy.

697
00:31:22,025 --> 00:31:23,761
Not a bad looking kid.

698
00:31:24,429 --> 00:31:25,931
I told you

699
00:31:25,999 --> 00:31:27,866
we weren't involved that way.

700
00:31:28,334 --> 00:31:30,707
The Dock Rats said
you two were getting pretty close.

701
00:31:30,774 --> 00:31:33,010
That is up until
Tommy got killed.

702
00:31:33,078 --> 00:31:35,378
And you got carted off
the Lancaster,

