715
00:32:04,303 --> 00:32:05,871
He was protecting me.

716
00:32:05,939 --> 00:32:07,673
No, he was trying to sweep it
under the rug.

717
00:32:07,741 --> 00:32:08,907
Erase it from history

718
00:32:08,908 --> 00:32:11,042
- by killing Tommy...
- You don't understand !

719
00:32:12,712 --> 00:32:15,680
