It was her choice.

720
00:32:15,748 --> 00:32:18,048
You're saying you were fine
with her keeping it ?

721
00:32:18,116 --> 00:32:19,149
Then ?

722
00:32:19,317 --> 00:32:21,318
No.

723
00:32:21,386 --> 00:32:24,288
If I could take it all back,

724
00:32:24,289 --> 00:32:26,189
handle things differently,

725
00:32:26,255 --> 00:32:28,156
