I did not kill that boy.

729
00:32:39,365 --> 00:32:41,535
If I just told him the truth...

730
00:32:42,902 --> 00:32:45,337
Maybe Tommy would
still be alive.

731
00:32:46,372 --> 00:32:48,573
Told him what, Molly ?

732
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:50,274
About the baby.

733
00:32:50,942 --> 00:32:53,009
What about the baby ?

734
00:32:54,477 --> 00:32:56,381
It wasn't Tommy's.

735
00:33:00,118 --> 00:33:01,418
