kissing me.

756
00:33:48,028 --> 00:33:50,295
Oh, God, I let him !

757
00:33:51,163 --> 00:33:52,764
Molly, who ?

758
00:33:54,732 --> 00:33:56,266
Dwight.

759
00:33:56,502 --> 00:33:58,503
It was Dwight.

760
00:33:58,970 --> 00:34:02,206
Tommy,
I'm pregnant.

761
00:34:05,709 --> 00:34:07,143
I tried to tell
him about it,

762
00:34:07,211 --> 00:34:09,145
but he won't even
look at me.

763
00:34:13,615 --> 00:34:15,050
Tommy, please,

764
00:34:15,118 --> 00:34:17,485
I'm so sorry.

765
00:34:19,621 --> 00:34:21,454
I don't know what I'm gonna do.

766
00:34:26,625 --> 00:34:28,625
I broke his heart.

767
00:34:30,794 --> 00:34:32,628
Mine, too.

768
00:34:32,696 --> 00:34:35,897
After you told him, he left...

769
00:34:35,964 --> 00:34:37,765
and headed back to the rink ?

770
00:34:39,267 --> 00:34:43,569
